finals.term:
The value of this field is "term and termination" only, nothing else. The following fields are also excluded from the value:

1. Confidential Information - any and all nonpublic information concerning or arising from Discloser's business;
2. Affiliates - any other entities that controls, is controlled by, or is under common control with Discloser in connection with its business;
3. Trade secret - any trade secret used, developed or acquired by Discloser in connection with its business; and
4. Termination or expiration
